content: Hi all, if we had a successful conversation in spanish but also want to mark the voter as such for any future calls - is there a way to do both of those things? I was able to confirm that they are voting for Harris. Seemed so based on searches here but wanted to check. Thank you!
Since the call was successful just mark it that way and in the future if he gets a call from someone who doesnt speak spanish then it can be marked that way
